+    // plain *mandatory* action (Sacrifice, Mill, Destroy, …) whose rider is a
+    // SEPARATE SENTENCE ("Sacrifice it. If you do, create Marit Lage.") has no
+    // such hook — and per CR 608.2c that sentence is the next printed
